@startuml C3_meetings_base
title C3. 미팅 생성/상세/검색

actor User
participant "app-service" as SVC
database "PostgreSQL\n(Meeting)" as PG

== 생성 ==
User -> SVC: POST /api/meetings\n{title, description, date, time, place, maxMembers, rules, tags[], joinFormId?, thumbnailId?}
SVC -> SVC: 토큰/바디 검증
SVC -> PG: INSERT meeting (...)
SVC --> User: 201 CREATED {success:true, data:{id:"m_123"}}

== 상세 ==
User -> SVC: GET /api/meetings/{id}
SVC -> PG: SELECT meeting + host + members + stats
alt 비공개/권한 없음
  SVC --> User: 403 FORBIDDEN
  return
end
alt 미존재
  SVC --> User: 404 NOT_FOUND
  return
end
SVC --> User: 200 OK {success:true, data:{...}}

== 검색 ==
User -> SVC: GET /api/meetings?keyword=...&tag=...&dateFrom=...&sort=latest&page=1&size=20
SVC -> PG: SELECT ... WHERE filters... ORDER BY ... LIMIT/OFFSET
alt 결과 없음
  SVC --> User: 200 OK {success:true, data:[]}
else 결과 있음
  SVC --> User: 200 OK {success:true, data:[{id:"m_123", title:"..."}]}
end
@enduml
